snippet: Jermaine Taylor and Calen Carr scored in the first half to lead the Dynamo to a 2-0 win over the visiting Red Bulls, extending Houston’s winning streak to five games.
abstract: Houston Dynamo defeat the New York Red Bulls, 2-0, in major league soccer action.
lead_paragraph: Jermaine Taylor and Calen Carr scored in the first half to lead the Dynamo to a 2-0 win over the visiting Red Bulls, extending Houston’s winning streak to five games.
